Package: python-espeakng
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, espeak-ng, espeak-ng-data
Suggests: python-python-espeakng-doc
Description: Some simple wrappers around eSpeak NG (Python 2)
 Some simple wrappers around eSpeak NG intended to make using this excellent TTS
 for waveform and IPA generation as convenient as possible.
 Target audience are developers who would like to use eSpeak NG as-is for speech
 synthesis in their Python application on GNU/Linux operating systems.  <insert
 long description, indented with spaces>
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 2.

